People aged 70 and over and those who are clinically extremely vulnerable can now book their #COVID19 #vaccine.
 
Choose a time and location that suits at https://t.co/ysFRmXl8Jb or call 119 for free anytime between 7am-11pm.
 
If a slot is not available, you can call your GP. https://t.co/trkEDN0mll
